data.description: Have you ever just entered a home and felt like you were home? Well, you will when you enter 40 Landoe Lane. If that amazing blue front door doesn't pique your interest, wait until you see the space this home provides! This 4 bed, 2 bath home, has 2, yes 2, living rooms, perfect for entertaining or spreading out. An amazing, updated kitchen sits at the top of the stairs with a spacious living room. From the kitchen exit through a sliding glass door out to the covered deck, overlooking the HUGE backyard, that was just re-seeded. 2 Bedrooms and 1 full bath are also on the upper level. Taking a trip down the stairs, enter living room number two, with an additional 2 bedrooms and a full bath. Laundry facilities are also located on the lower floor, in a well sized laundry room. Outdoors, both yards are fenced, the 1 car garage has access from the home and the carport adds the perfect amount of extra covered parking. This home is in close proximity to schools, shopping and entertainment. This home really does have it all. Short commute to all surrounding military installations.
